725286f-a.title: Queens: 38th Street - Astoria Boulevard
725286f-a.text:
38th Street, north from Astoria Boulevard, showing demolition
for the construction of Grand Central Parkway.
View 2 is at the corner of 24th Avenue.
P. L. Sperr  September 20, 1934
NO REPRODUCTIONS  Views 1,2
